data.meta_description: The THE KING OF FIGHTERS ‘95 soundtrack on a single colored record or on physical CD. This is an open pre-order for a limited time.PRE-ORDERS CLOSE ON SUNDAY, APRIL 18TH 2021 AT 11:59PM EASTERN TIME Features newly remastered analog and digital tracks, as well as a booklet containing archival artwork and liner notes by
